# Next.js Guidelines

## Routing
- Prefer App Router if `app/` exists; otherwise use Pages Router under `pages/`

## Data Fetching
- Server-side: use native fetch and caching options
- Client-side: only when necessary; keep components minimal

## Components
- Use functional components, typed props
- Avoid heavy logic in components; extract helpers

## Performance
- Enable image optimization; prefer WebP sources
- Configure `revalidate` where appropriate

## SEO
- Provide metadata where possible (title, description)